      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WHISPERED (3) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage a neck away in second (34.88). Top prospect. MAGIC LOKI (1) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at this track over 600m behind Ascend Ecstatic (35.04) in a Grade 4/5. Was a winner prior to that. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from four starts. Must be included in calculations. EXTRAVAGANZA (7) looks close to another win after finishing second from Box 8 last time (29.71) at Sandown. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Hard to beat again. LUNA'S GIRL (2) saluted last start after racing on the speed. Sure to run well again.",
